episodes.title: Heavens Gate: The Definitive Story (cult documentary)
episodes.description:
Documentary from 2007 about the suicide UFO cult Heaven's Gate. 

Tells the tale of the Heaven's Gate cult, from Haight-Ashbury back in the early 70's, up until the fateful day when they drank poison in the late 90's. There are interviews with a variety of different people, including former members, as well as cult experts Rick Ross and Janja Lalich

Marshall Applewhite.
